{"tid":900174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾堆中翻找用過衛生棉　「水煮M巾」代替毒品帶來輕飄飄幻覺","createTime":"2018-11-13T04:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T07:36:03.000Z","uid":150685,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3905a4cfc534c157d75d507177c47d8a81f17d","tid":900174,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2205000/2207063/M_thumb_20181113_ch_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2205000%2F2207063%2FM_thumb_20181113_ch_1024.png&h=e3b31da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衛生巾經煮沸後會有毒素氯氣（chlorine），飲後與吸毒感覺相似。<br />\n<br />\n印尼吸毒問題嚴重，據印尼大學2016年研究顯示，當地吸毒者達640萬人，每日約有33人死於濫用毒品。當地年輕人近年興起一種不可思議的毒品，就是在垃圾堆中找出使用過的衛生巾，放入熱水中煮後再把「M巾水」飲落肚，號稱可以代替毒品，帶來輕飄飄的感覺！<br />\n<br />\n緝毒局官員：毒素氯氣帶來幻覺<br />\n<br />\n據《雅加達郵報》報道，印尼警方日前逮捕一群年輕人，他們以「M巾水」模仿吸毒的感覺。他們會先在垃圾堆中翻找用過的衛山巾，然後用水煮過後，待涼掉後就喝掉。<br />\n<br />\n飲用「M巾水」雖然聽起來很噁心，但印尼國家緝毒局的官員蘇比蘭多（Adj. Sr. Comr. Suprinarto）指衛生巾經煮沸後，水中會含有毒素氯氣（chlorine），飲後會有「飄飄然」及飛起來的幻覺，和吸毒的感覺很相似，而且也比真實的毒品便宜。<br />\n<br />\n印尼警方目前已經在雅加達、西爪哇、中爪哇各地逮捕了多名吸食毒品年輕人，當中多名被捕人士都以類似方法「吸毒」。<br />\n<br />\n混合濫用驅蚊劑和咳藥水飲醉<br />\n<br />\n事實上這種吸毒方法並不是新現象，早在2016年，印尼警方已經查獲類似事件，在2017年起案例更有增加的跡象，但現時當地仍未有相關法律管理。除此之外，有青少年也會找酒精的代替品，企圖得到飲醉的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2207063/%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%A0%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%BF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%A3%89%E3%80%80%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E7%85%AEM%E5%B7%BE%E3%80%8D%E4%BB%A3%E6%9B%BF%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E8%BC%95%E9%A3%84%E9%A3%84%E5%B9%BB%E8%A6%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2207063%2F%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E5%25A0%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2589%25BE%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25A3%2589%25E3%2580%2580%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2585%25AEM%25E5%25B7%25BE%25E3%2580%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%259B%25BF%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%25A3%2584%25E9%25A3%2584%25E5%25B9%25BB%25E8%25A6%25BA&d=FOSiJIdA3EVv5kz%2FnXbgJQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=829c2662\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2207063/%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E5%A0%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%BF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%A8%E9%81%8E%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%A3%89%E3%80%80%E3%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E7%85%AEM%E5%B7%BE%E3%80%8D%E4%BB%A3%E6%9B%BF%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E8%BC%95%E9%A3%84%E9%A3%84%E5%B9%BB%E8%A6%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n索M巾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e286e3e2933b467c4724b37ffcbbf0f7c1124ed0","tid":900174,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"印尼人個iq係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94995dc4e3df03213ab66e34a30327de1fda0a2c","tid":900174,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"氯氣（chlorine）係咪即係泳池個隻?"},{"pid":"de0a2eef925e55bde17a05f8eba8b435d1a6bb08","tid":900174,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"越近赤道d人越on9"},{"pid":"ffa146d673454e0515d955089555ae487fc78069","tid":900174,"uid":91813,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"94995dc4e3df03213ab66e34a30327de1fda0a2c","tid":900174,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"氯氣（chlorine）係咪即係泳池個隻?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"係 就係佢令你係泳池輕飄飄浮得起"},{"pid":"c2afa8dba5adde808e019ac593d954b95bd99af4","tid":900174,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"乜印尼咁鍾意玩經血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c47f7b952512122b8331a56134a9e62072e8dfa","tid":900174,"uid":53126,"like":3,"dis